## 15. Data Breach Notification

### 15.1 Our Commitment

In the event of a data breach affecting your information, we will:
- Notify affected users within 72 hours
- Describe the nature of the breach
- Explain steps being taken
- Provide guidance on protective measures

### 15.2 Breach Response

We will:
- Investigate the breach immediately
- Implement additional security measures
- Report to appropriate authorities if required

## 16. Transparency Report

Upon request, we can provide:
- Number of data deletion requests processed
- Types of data collected
- Data retention statistics
- Third-party service usage

## 17. Your Consent

By using Grims Guide, you consent to:
- Data collection as described
- Data processing for service provision
- Use of third-party services (Discord, Google, Blizzard)
- Storage and retention practices outlined

You can withdraw consent by:
- Removing the Bot from your server
- Requesting data deletion

